name: Cosmic love - Rayah & Xakan - Making of
description:
The making of the original picture, only airdropped to everyone with the picture.

Before the The Blind Idiot God dreamed of the Universe there was nothing. And before there was nothing there were monsters, they've been push away to the boundaries of creation but their presence can be seen in the stars like a bright omen.

This universe use to move around them, their very thought used to bend the reality around them, they used to be the very heart of this reality.

As the love between them increase the influence they had on this universe grew too.

Until their burning passion destroyed everything and anything around them until the next one.

Inspired by Lovecraft Pantheon and by Xayah & Rakan from League of Legends.
